Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.91,0:23:07.22,OP ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}就算只是收藏在心底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.29,0:23:09.05,OP ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}Search for my life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.19,0:23:13.39,OP ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}总有一天还会再相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.49,0:23:20.26,OP ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}就是喜欢你那清澈的双眼现在
